{"tid":1628591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[對準目標] 裝修商家先會驚 先會比壓力政府","createTime":"2019-10-06T03:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T08:40:50.000Z","uid":165213,"like":25,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b5a97b4ca15b318e48fd48477be313f5b44c1776","tid":1628591,"uid":165213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:46:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">裝修商家先會驚 先會比壓力政府 <br />\n呢家十八區開花 班狗做唔切就開始轉風向話無用<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母<br />\n呢啲先叫做實事 目標係中資黑底好清晰<br />\n呢啲先確實影響到大商家同政府</span></span>"},{"pid":"dac24ae94af240a23af2c1d7627de46cd2465bb7","tid":1628591,"uid":284317,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:49:03.000Z","msg":"鄭立：對準政權是錯誤的；成功就是香港的東西的滲透度被最低化<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1607759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1607759</a>"},{"pid":"bf7a1fafd6ad07e2a2271df11d03afd6002b2d46","tid":1628591,"uid":284317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:49:18.000Z","msg":"經過咁漫長嘅對話，我希望大家都明白，要打倒政權，唔在於果個行動睇落係咪「對準政權」<br />\n<br />\n[終極攻略]點樣做會贏? 一齊學習戰爭同戰略<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eeJBzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eeJBzT</a>"},{"pid":"92c54a3fcbe738b10c56e082fcc335dbd8ff2cf4","tid":1628591,"uid":165213,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:50:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好剩係聽人講 唔好比五毛帶風向<br />\n最簡單 用腦諗下 站在商家政府角度 點樣先會令佢地驚？<br />\n就係無生意 無人返工 呢家手足正正做緊呢樣野<br />\n目標好清晰 外國人都明我地做緊咩<br />\n仲割乜撚野 </span></span>"},{"pid":"82cd62ac78bf422d9a8d769dbda7e5a4bd38466c","tid":1628591,"uid":165213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:51:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2a0204a042955bace25ba1e3ef018250829fb75a","tid":1628591,"uid":165213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:52:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b10cb61